f=Brand Studio/lena/custom/humanic-writing/assets/ai-tells-catalog.md · h1:Tells Compressed Catalog (humanic-writing, Phase=Adapted concise-writing's reference (l4ci/latticework), whose catalog draws Wikipedia's "Signs writing" (WikiProject Cleanup) concision canon (Strunk White, Zinsser, Williams). Judge CLUSTERS: any single tell weak evidence human produce; several together confession. cluster found, rewrite sentence around concrete claim hides never delete trigger word leave stump. · h2:The clusters=**Inflated significance legacy.** "marks pivotal moment," "stands/serves testament," "plays vital role," "reflects broader," "evolving landscape," "leaves indelible mark." Puffs small fact grand trend. State fact., **Promotional adjectives.** "vibrant," "rich," "nestled," "in heart of," "breathtaking," "must-visit," "renowned," "groundbreaking." Brochure tone. Cut, replace specific., **Fake-depth -ing tails.** "…, highlighting the…," "…, ensuring…," "…, reflecting…," "…, showcasing…." Tacked-on analysis. Usually deletable whole., **Copula avoidance.** "serves as," "boasts," "features," "represents" "is"/"has" do. Restore plain verb., **Rule three, false ranges, synonym cycling.** Forced triplets ("innovation, inspiration, insight"), "from isn't real scale, noun renamed sentence. Pick one, drop padding., **Negative parallelism tailing negations.** "It's it's Y," "not merely a…, a…," clipped tags like "no guessing," "no wasted motion." Make positive claim directly., **Filler hedging.** "it important note that," "in order to," "at point time," "the ability to," stacked maybes. Cut, one word means same., **Signposting meta.** "let's dive in," "here's what you need know," "in section will." Announcing instead doing. Delete thing., **Aphorism formulas false authority.** language Y," tool mirror," "the real question is," "at core," "what really matters." Sounds profound, says little. concrete point., **Corporate buzzwords.** "delve," "leverage," "landscape," "robust," "streamline," "facilitate," "comprehensive," "empower," "seamless." voice's actual word, nothing., **Chatbot artifacts servility.** "Great question!", "Certainly!", hope helps," "You're absolutely right." Correspondence pasted content. Cut entirely., **Structural uniformity.** sentence 15–20 words; paragraph topic-sentence three supports transition; symmetrical bullets; perfect header parallelism; transition addiction (Moreover/Furthermore/Additionally opening paragraph). Break rhythm: short punches, one longer flow, fragment voice allows., **Tonal flatness.** opinions, contractions, equal weight everything, zero risk. Inject voice's stance emphasis (Phase 3), generic edge., **Mechanical formatting.** Emoji headings, boldface key phrase, Title Case Headings, bullet lists item bold-header-plus-colon. Strip plain text unless voice guide says otherwise. · h2:Scan template=`FINGERPRINT SCAN \· Clusters found: [list, with one example each] \· Buzzword count: N \· Rhythm: uniform/varied \· Hedging density: high/low \· Contractions: present/absent vs voice rule \· Opinions/stance: present/absent \· Verdict: [reads generated / borderline / reads human] — basis: [clusters, not single hits]` · h2:two rules govern use=**Rewrite around underlying claim.** cluster hiding concrete point find it, say plainly voice. **Voice guide wins over catalog.** brand's guide requires pattern listed (rare, logged such), guide governs flag conflict humanic-writing's fallback.